{
  "stem": "18450.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 404.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had not suitcases, but a little, you know, whatever it was in the hand we took.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we went in on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother took me in through the window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the train was covered with all kind of greens, you know, because-- and we didn't know where it going.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we just on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was mostly like cattle, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- what they call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Cattle car?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, cattle car, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't, you know-- if somebody had a piece of bread, you shared.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You did share.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were very sharing, yeah, because everybody thought that's the last day of their life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But some-- I would say, in Russian, some of the farmers, they bringed out, not too much, but whatever they had, they-- they brought up a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So natural, everybody had a-- just a crumb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, who had money?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went up the first, we stayed in Stalingrad, near Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a place-- a fish, you know, on the Volga.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stayed there a few weeks and worked, you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We catched fish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, you don't have to catch them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You just, you know, took them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Germans came there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You hear that they're coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I didn't stay again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We just went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And luckily, we got another train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you didn't know where you're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody knew, absolutely no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They're just cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But this time, was a-- a farmer there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he gave us a little bit too of some bread or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we took with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we traveled a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
